===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|stelthe}}, from {{inh|en|ang|stǣlþ}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*stēliþō}}<ref>{{R:Online Etymology Dictionary|accessdate=31 July 2018}}</ref>, equivalent to {{suf|en|steal|th}}. Compare {{cog|ang|stalu|t=theft, stealth}}, {{cog|goh|stāla|t=theft}}, {{cog|de|Diebstahl|t=theft}}.

